name: IncensedAnimals
description:
A Fun Filled 2d Blow up Game. Incensed animals Jungle is ruled by different animals sections. The rulers never fought with each other. On a fateful night a ufo appeared out of no where and started mutating the animals. They have also taken few of the rulers as the prisoners'. in order to save the  jungle you need to kill the aliens before they completely wipe animals out. They are mutating the animals after they have feasted on them. 

You can download The pre-alpha game to play offline Incensedanimals
